umn-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f8435d0\" data-id=\"f8435d0\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00e941b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"00e941b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>English Speech and Delivery<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p>Do you lose your confidence while conversing in English? Do you always find yourself at loss of words whenever you wanted to give your presentation? Do you always find yourself fumbling whenever you were asked to do sales pitch? Is facing an interview a nightmare? Solution to all these is \u201cEnglish Speech and Delivery\u201d class.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); font-size: 1rem;\">English is a language that is widely used by people all over the world. The importance of English language is increasing day in and day out. India is the world\u2019s second-largest English-speaking country. Though Hindi is the mother tongue of India, English is the preferred medium of instruction in schools and colleges. In most places in India, the documents are made in English.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); font-size: 1rem;\">Nowadays, Indian aspirants have the urge to study abroad and make a career there. To get admission in foreign universities, it is imperative to have command on the English language and communication. Children should have proficiency in both written and verbal English. Many countries also make it mandatory to clear the IELTS &#8211; English Proficiency Test.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p>India is a country with diverse languages. Job seekers move from East to West or North to South seeking jobs and the common official communicative language used is English. An organization looks for candidates with exceptional communication skills and a good command over English. Today companies have international clients, which makes it even more important to master the English language.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p>We @ Brahmas SiteHRMS help you to overcome all the worries by giving you ample practical sessions. Confidence building, Personality development, Public speaking, are some of the crucial elements that we focus on. We care for our students future, and this motivates us to work hard. Guiding them in the right direction is predominantly the prerequisite concern that makes us an edge over others.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8872a20 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8872a20\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-75271f5\" data-id=\"75271f5\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\